<LI><FONT SIZE=+2>ping host_name</FONT></LI>

<UL>
<LI><FONT SIZE=+1>-s : send ICMP echo packet every second</FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT SIZE=+1>-lRV: trace route</FONT></LI>
</UL>

<LI><FONT SIZE=+2>netstat </FONT></LI>

<UL>
<LI><FONT SIZE=+1>-r : show routing table</FONT></LI>

<LI><FONT SIZE=+1>-s : show protocol statistics</FONT></LI>
</UL>

<LI><FONT SIZE=+2>traceroute host_name</FONT></LI>

<UL>
<LI><FONT SIZE=+1>-t : specify quality of service (low delay = 16, high
throughput=8)</FONT></LI>
</UL>

<LI><FONT SIZE=+2>ifconfig -a shows current status of network interfaces</FONT>
</LI>
